title: Strange Fedfellows
description: It’s been 6 years since a member of the Federal Reserve improperly leaked information to an analyst. Kate & Luigi wonder what's really changed. Is the Fed still too cozy with big banks, the media and others with a financial stake in monetary policy?
author: uchicagopodcasts@gmail.com (Chicago Booth Review)
